<section class="hero">

<h1>
Non-coding <span>RNA</span>
</h1>

<p>
Non-coding RNA research explores RNA molecules that do not encode proteins but regulate gene expression, chromatin state, RNA stability, translation, signaling pathways, and disease-associated molecular programs.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
  <img
    src="/research-non-coding-rna-hero-v1.png"
